{"tid":622079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死廢老擅闖九巴員工廁所被斷正 爆粗狂罵：屌你老母臭閪!我唔急尿㗎！","createTime":"2018-04-08T23:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T10:46:25.000Z","uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1351565e7dc3e76698c423df2e4799ebddf62a44","tid":622079,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T23:58:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180409/58048010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F58048010&d=mSnZCbuwGwLGEtgLd%2FnI7R4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=c6e76499\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F58048010&h=540a0cdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180409/58048010</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180408/large/1523181721_9df8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180408%2Flarge%2F1523181721_9df8.png&h=20077897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴士車長常遭躁客辱罵、不停受氣，沒想到除了車廂，站頭休息地都成靶場！網上瘋傳一條短片，一名阿伯在藍田滙景巴士總站的九巴員工專用的洗手間如廁，車長入內要求阿伯離開，但阿伯不停粗口橫飛，先罵車長「垃圾」、「有咩資格講嘢呀」，更罵「九巴公司執笠啦冚家X」，但又稱自己「唔急尿㗎」。<br />\n<br />\n車長遂指向門上告示牌，稱「九巴員工專用」，惟「員工」兩字被貼紙遮蓋。阿伯離開洗手間，但又突然關燈，車長即表示「喂，唔好熄燈啦師兄用緊呀」，阿伯即罵「唔X洗用啦，垃圾嚟㗎」。阿伯情緒失控，不停以粗口辱罵車長，車長則勸告對方冷靜並稱「係員工專用㗎」，阿伯隨即大罵「係狗X專用，唔係九巴專用」，車長感無奈表示：「啱呀狗X專用，入去用吖嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n有車長表示，公司規定員工廁所因保險問題不外借，但就有市民當作公廁自出自入。不少網民認為阿伯野蠻，稱讚車長「EQ高」，有人建議九巴應在員工廁所安裝拍卡門鎖，以防有同類事件發生。<br />\n<br />\n網民留言 <br />\n●Bess Wong：廢老！又要威又要「帶頭」虧<br />\n●Chan Sze Ching：吾知點解睇到個呀叔咁炆好想笑<br />\n●No Tsang：條老鬼系咪腎虧加失禁呀，你唔俾佢入去解決隨時系門口攪掂wo<br />\n●Yim Sheung Yeung：九巴先進啲啦。換職員拍咭門鎖啦 。周街都有廢死佬坑。小小員工福利都唔到。成日只識增加車長壓力。<br />\n●Tommy Tung：佢痾極都痾唔出尿，比人發現左先咁撚嬲姐，阿伯，去睇醫生啦，下次咪唔洗咁尷尬<br />\n●Kai Hong Oscar Yu：廢老咁多時間真係社會不幸&hellip;&hellip;佢地就不能好好的在家嗎？沒廁所水嗎？有公廁唔搵係要咁頑皮&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">死廢老唔急尿做乜鳩入廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想做免費勞工幫手洗屎坑呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"4c0537748d19555995ba962ac3a4159a6bcc5761","tid":622079,"uid":140516,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:00:24.000Z","msg":"阿伯肚餓啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a317d67eb1c8aba48d2f295f5b8c0a23aa72eb88","tid":622079,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:04:28.000Z","msg":"起件廢老底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99df2d33c784956393b7cbe3e4e1250f7140a21","tid":622079,"uid":38777,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:06:16.000Z","msg":"廢老真係香港毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7073a44561c2b8e29e0fbc6b504af579f560f78","tid":622079,"uid":143260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:10:57.000Z","msg":"唔係所有老人家都係咁廢柴，而係班死廢人全部都老撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f2fe72e9e6281d4e791049a19a6ffeb16054e8","tid":622079,"uid":34884,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:17:56.000Z","msg":"阿伯情緒失控，不停以粗口辱罵車長，車長則勸告對方冷靜並稱「係員工專用㗎」，阿伯隨即大罵「係狗X專用，唔係九巴專用」，車長感無奈表示：「啱呀狗X專用，入去用吖嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1819214c3253119f9d6319f3037795afc49120c5","tid":622079,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:44:27.00